A Very simple URL shortener with the function to delete expired shortened URL's.
The Query of the database and the settings for the database connection is included in the c.php file.
You should change the url http://localhost/url in the index.php file to the directory where your url shortener script files are.
If you want to you can set the expire dat by changing +1 (on line 40 in index.php) to the day(s) it will stay in the database.